---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Scleral Lenses in Tijuana | Keratoconus Specialists | Ópticas Jarmar"
  description="Specialists in scleral contact lenses for keratoconus, corneal transplant, and irregular cornea in Tijuana. Ópticas Jarmar."
>
  <style>
    :root { --bg: #071A3E; --surface: #0D2B6B; --accent: #3A8FE0; }

    .hero { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%); color: #fff; padding: 100px 20px 80px; text-align: center; }
    .hero-tag { display: inline-block; background: rgba(58,143,224,0.2); border: 1px solid var(--accent); color: var(--accent); border-radius: 100px; padding: 6px 18px; font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 24px; }
    .hero h1 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .hero h1 span { color: var(--accent); }
    .hero p { font-size: 1.15rem; opacity: 0.85; max-width: 640px; margin: 0 auto 36px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .btn-cta { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 100px; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; text-decoration: none; transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.2s; }
    .btn-cta:hover { opacity: 0.9; transform: translateY(-2px); }

    .container { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 20px; }
    .section { padding: 72px 20px; }
    .section:nth-child(even) { background: #f7f9fc; }
    .section-title { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2.2rem); font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .section-title span { color: var(--accent); }
    .section-sub { color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 36px; }

    .que-son-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; align-items: start; }
    @media (max-width: 640px) { .que-son-inner { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .que-son-texto p { color: #4a5568; line-height: 1.75; font-size: 1.05rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .stat-row { display: flex; gap: 20px; margin-top: 8px; }
    .stat { background: var(--surface); color: #fff; border-radius: 16px; padding: 20px; text-align: center; flex: 1; }
    .stat strong { display: block; font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); }
    .stat span { font-size: 0.85rem; opacity: 0.85; line-height: 1.4; }

    .condiciones { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .condicion { background: #fff; border-radius: 18px; border: 1.5px solid rgba(58,143,224,0.25); padding: 28px 24px; }
    .condicion-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 14px; display: block; }
    .condicion h4 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 1.05rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .condicion p { color: #4a5568; font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    .proceso { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; position: relative; }
    .proceso::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 22px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px; background: rgba(58,143,224,0.3); }
    .paso { display: flex; gap: 24px; align-items: flex-start; padding-bottom: 36px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
    .paso:last-child { padding-bottom: 0; }
    .paso-num { background: var(--accent); color: #fff; border-radius: 50%; width: 44px; height: 44px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .paso h4 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; color: var(--bg); margin-bottom: 6px; font-size: 1.05rem; }
    .paso p { color: #4a5568; font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.65; }

    .testimonios { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
    .testimonio { background: var(--surface); color: #fff; border-radius: 18px; padding: 28px 24px; }
    .testimonio-stars { color: #fbbf24; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-bottom: 14px; letter-spacing: 2px; }
    .testimonio p { font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.7; opacity: 0.9; margin-bottom: 16px; font-style: italic; }
    .testimonio-autor { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--accent); }

    .cta-section { background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--bg) 0%, var(--surface) 100%); color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 80px 20px; }
    .cta-section h2 { font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .cta-section p { font-size: 1.1rem; opacity: 0.85; margin-bottom: 36px; max-width: 560px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; }

    .back-link { display: block; text-align: center; padding: 28px; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.95rem; font-weight: 600; }
    .back-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="hero-tag">Specialty · Tijuana</span>
      <h1><span>Scleral Lenses</span><br>in Tijuana</h1>
      <p>Over 10 years as leaders in scleral contact lenses in Mexico. A solution for those who thought there was no solution.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+information+about+scleral+lenses+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Evaluate my case →
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What are <span>scleral lenses</span>?</h2>
      <div class="que-son-inner">
        <div class="que-son-texto">
          <p>Scleral lenses are large-diameter contact lenses that rest on the sclera (the white of the eye), without touching the cornea. This creates a saline reservoir between the lens and the cornea.</p>
          <p>Unlike conventional contact lenses, sclerals are ideal for irregular or damaged corneas where soft or standard rigid lenses don't work.</p>
          <p>The result is crisp, comfortable vision even in the most complex cases.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="stat-row">
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>+10</strong>
              <span>years of specialty</span>
            </div>
            <div class="stat">
              <strong>98%</strong>
              <span>fitting success rate</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Conditions we <span>treat</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Scleral lenses are the treatment of choice for various complex corneal conditions.</p>
      <div class="condiciones">
        <div class="condicion">
          <span class="condicion-icon">🔺</span>
          <h4>Keratoconus</h4>
          <p>Progressive cone-shaped corneal deformation that prevents clear vision with conventional lenses.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="condicion">
          <span class="condicion-icon">🔬</span>
          <h4>Corneal transplant</h4>
          <p>Optimal visual recovery post-transplant by compensating for graft irregularity for maximum acuity.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="condicion">
          <span class="condicion-icon">⚡</span>
          <h4>Post-refractive surgery</h4>
          <p>For patients unsatisfied with LASIK or blade surgery results. We restore your vision.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="condicion">
          <span class="condicion-icon">💧</span>
          <h4>Severe dry eye</h4>
          <p>The saline reservoir in scleral lenses keeps the cornea hydrated throughout wear.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">The fitting <span>process</span></h2>
      <p class="section-sub">Scleral lens fitting is a personalized process performed with high-precision corneal topography equipment.</p>
      <div class="proceso">
        <div class="paso">
          <div class="paso-num">1</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Initial evaluation</h4>
            <p>We review your medical history, corneal topography, refraction, and ocular health to determine if you are a candidate for scleral lenses.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="paso">
          <div class="paso-num">2</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Trial fitting</h4>
            <p>We select the appropriate trial lens and evaluate the fit, corneal clearance, and visual acuity achieved.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="paso">
          <div class="paso-num">3</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Custom order</h4>
            <p>We order your lens with the exact parameters measured in consultation to ensure the best possible fit.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="paso">
          <div class="paso-num">4</div>
          <div>
            <h4>Training & follow-up</h4>
            <p>We teach you the correct insertion technique and schedule follow-up visits to optimize your adaptation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">What our <span>patients say</span></h2>
      <div class="testimonios">
        <div class="testimonio">
          <div class="testimonio-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>"I had advanced keratoconus and thought I'd never see clearly again. With the scleral lenses from Jarmar I got my life back. 100% recommended."</p>
          <span class="testimonio-autor">— Carlos M., Tijuana</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonio">
          <div class="testimonio-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>"After my corneal transplant I couldn't find anyone who could help me properly. Here they gave me a real solution. The process was very professional."</p>
          <span class="testimonio-autor">— Ana L., Tijuana</span>
        </div>
        <div class="testimonio">
          <div class="testimonio-stars">★★★★★</div>
          <p>"I came from San Diego specifically for the fitting. Completely worth it. Jarmar's team is the most specialized I've found anywhere near the border."</p>
          <span class="testimonio-autor">— R.V., San Diego</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Do you think you're a candidate for scleral lenses?</h2>
      <p>Contact us to evaluate your case. We serve patients from San Diego, Tijuana, and the entire US–Mexico border region.</p>
      <a href="https://wa.me/526645791970?text=Hello%2C+I%27d+like+information+about+scleral+lenses+at+%C3%93pticas+Jarmar+Tijuana." target="_blank" class="btn-cta">
        Book via WhatsApp
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <a href="/en/tijuana/" class="back-link">← Back to Tijuana</a>
</BaseLayout>
